</li>
<li data-start="820" data-end="883">
<p data-start="822" data-end="883">Why event logs are insufficient without monotone commitment</p>
</li>
<li data-start="884" data-end="954">
<p data-start="886" data-end="954">Distinction between replayable traces and non-invertible histories</p>
</li>
</ul>
