<p data-start="4850" data-end="4878"><strong data-start="4850" data-end="4878">Does not reduce ambition</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="4879" data-end="4922">
<p data-start="4881" data-end="4922"><strong data-start="4881" data-end="4922">Increases reviewer trust dramatically</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="4923" data-end="4982">
<p data-start="4925" data-end="4982">Makes the paper look <em data-start="4946" data-end="4958">inevitable</em> rather than speculative</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="4984" data-end="5006">A reviewer will think:</p>
<blockquote data-start="5008" data-end="5098">
<p data-start="5010" data-end="5098">“This author knows exactly which traditions they are extending — and where they depart.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="5100" data-end="5122">That’s the sweet spot.</p>
