<p data-start="2182" data-end="2304">Below is <strong data-start="2191" data-end="2209">your Section 1</strong>, rewritten <em data-start="2221" data-end="2241">verbatim in spirit</em>, with <strong data-start="2248" data-end="2303">citations added exactly where reviewers expect them</strong>.</p>
