<hr data-start="287" data-end="290">
<h2 data-start="292" data-end="338">1. What you are about to do (operationally)</h2>
<p data-start="340" data-end="353">Your plan is:</p>
<ol data-start="355" data-end="818">
<li data-start="355" data-end="513">
<p data-start="358" data-end="407">Maintain <strong data-start="367" data-end="384">two histories</strong> of the same document</p>
<ul data-start="411" data-end="513">
<li data-start="411" data-end="451">
