</li>
<li data-start="455" data-end="513">
<p data-start="457" data-end="513">Draft B: citation-integrated, structurally disciplined</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="515" data-end="693">
<p data-start="518" data-end="576">Perform a <strong data-start="528" data-end="555">line-by-line diff/merge</strong> using a Linux tool</p>
