<h2 data-start="2266" data-end="2342">Option C — Writing as Event-History (Reflective / Methodological Section)</h2>
<p data-start="2344" data-end="2425"><strong data-start="2344" data-end="2353">Goal:</strong> Make the <em data-start="2363" data-end="2386">method of composition</em> itself an explicit object of analysis.</p>
