<ul data-start="2446" data-end="2533">
<li data-start="2446" data-end="2498">
<p data-start="2448" data-end="2498">Writing as irreversible construction, not drafting</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2499" data-end="2533">
<p data-start="2501" data-end="2533">Parallel to cognition and agency</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="2535" data-end="2562">C2. Drafts as Histories</h3>
<ul data-start="2563" data-end="2620">
<li data-start="2563" data-end="2588">
<p data-start="2565" data-end="2588">Each version as a world</p>
