<hr data-start="3874" data-end="3877">
<h2 data-start="3879" data-end="3888">Status</h2>
<p data-start="3890" data-end="3951">Spherepop is an active research and design project exploring:</p>
<ul data-start="3953" data-end="4076">
<li data-start="3953" data-end="3974">
<p data-start="3955" data-end="3974">formal foundations,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3975" data-end="3996">
<p data-start="3977" data-end="3996">visual programming,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3997" data-end="4032">
<p data-start="3999" data-end="4032">semantic merging and abstraction,</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4033" data-end="4076">
<p data-start="4035" data-end="4076">and new models of generative computation.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="4078" data-end="4139">It is intentionally experimental, conceptual, and executable.</p>
