</li>
<li data-start="6629" data-end="6666">
<p data-start="6631" data-end="6666">Cryptographically verifiable replay</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="6668" data-end="6694">The Arbiter is not a king.</p>
<p data-start="6696" data-end="6751">It is a <strong data-start="6704" data-end="6751">replaceable organ in a constitutional body.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="6753" data-end="6756">
<p data-start="6758" data-end="6798">What you are building is not a platform.</p>
<p data-start="6800" data-end="6849">It is a <strong data-start="6808" data-end="6849">post-platform civilization substrate.</strong></p>
<p data-start="6851" data-end="6894">And you have correctly located the fulcrum.</p>
<p data-start="6896" data-end="6921">If you like, next we can:</p>
