<h3 data-start="3155" data-end="3202">Why this bibliography is structurally right</h3>
<p data-start="3204" data-end="3262">This set triangulates your argument from three directions:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="3264" data-end="3671" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="3264" data-end="3294"><tr data-start="3264" data-end="3294"><th data-start="3264" data-end="3273" data-col-size="sm">Domain</th><th data-start="3273" data-end="3294" data-col-size="sm">Function in paper</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="3324" data-end="3671"><tr data-start="3324" data-end="3380"><td data-start="3324" data-end="3350" data-col-size="sm">Akerlof, Varian, Zuboff</td><td data-start="3350" data-end="3380" data-col-size="sm">Platform political economy</td></tr><tr data-start="3381" data-end="3430"><td data-start="3381" data-end="3408" data-col-size="sm">Lessig, Galloway, Winner</td><td data-start="3408" data-end="3430" data-col-size="sm">Code as governance</td></tr><tr data-start="3431" data-end="3498"><td data-start="3431" data-end="3455" data-col-size="sm">Lamport, FLP, Herlihy</td><td data-start="3455" data-end="3498" data-col-size="sm">Time &amp; causality in distributed systems</td></tr><tr data-start="3499" data-end="3568"><td data-start="3499" data-end="3538" data-col-size="sm">Heidegger, Deleuze, Ricoeur, Barbour</td><td data-start="3538" data-end="3568" data-col-size="sm">Ontology of time &amp; control</td></tr><tr data-start="3569" data-end="3625"><td data-start="3569" data-end="3587" data-col-size="sm">Needham, Meijer</td><td data-start="3587" data-end="3625" data-col-size="sm">Structural thinking in computation</td></tr><tr data-start="3626" data-end="3671"><td data-start="3626" data-end="3636" data-col-size="sm">Rollins</td><td data-start="3636" data-end="3671" data-col-size="sm">Psychoanalytic interface theory</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="